-- London's Gatwick Airport Has Been Closed While Snow Is Cleared From Runway
-- B y   M a r i a   E r m a k o v a
-- 2010-12-01T06:26:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-01/london-s-gatwick-airport-has-been-closed-while-snow-is-cleared-from-runway.html
London’s Gatwick airport runway is
currently closed to allow snow clearance, the airport said on
its website.  Flights will be “severely disrupted” due to current
weather conditions, Gatwick said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
